parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to replace Takata airbags can lead to explosions, injuries, and fatalities in the event of an accident, posing a significant risk to vehicle occupants.
symptoms: Airbag warning light illuminates
"Service Airbag" message appears on the dashboard
airbag deployment without warning or impact
and inability to schedule repair due to unavailability of replacement parts.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The lack of available replacement parts for Takata airbags prevents vehicle owners from having their vehicles repaired, leaving them at risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Dealerships unable to schedule repair due to unavailability of replacement parts
repeated notifications of recall without ability to repair
and inability to sell vehicle due to open recall.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Airbag Deployment without Warning or Impact
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Sudden airbag deployment without warning or impact can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities, and may also lead to unintended consequences such as whiplash.
symptoms: Airbag deployment without warning or impact
loss of control of the vehicle
and injuries to occupants.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause a range of issues, including loss of power steering, stalling, and malfunctioning of various systems, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Radio cutting out
door locks locking and unlocking on their own
air conditioning
cooled front seats
and defrost turning on and off
seats and airbag off light coming on
engine revving without power
warning messages saying "Service Stability System"
blind spot indicator failing intermittently
windshield wipers not staying on
cruise control failing
windows rolling up or down without warning
rear doors not locking and unlocking with remote
rear passenger lock not unlocking from key or button
stalling
and electrical issues giving error codes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The stalling and failure of the engine can cause loss of control, accidents, or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Engine stalling
loss of power
inability to shift gears
and warning messages saying "Service Stability System".

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the suspension system can cause loss of control, accidents, or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Suspension issues constantly
and warning messages saying "Service Stability System".

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden failure of the electronic power steering system can cause the steering wheel to seize or become difficult to turn, leading to loss of control, accidents, or fatalities, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: Loss of power steering while driving
sudden failure of power steering without warning
steering wheel becomes difficult to turn
"Service Steering" message displayed on the message board
corrosion of the power steering unit.
